name: Ty Kulick
text: Ordered delivery and they never showed up.  Called the manager, about an hour and a half after we ordered, and they said it would be there anytime.  We waited an additional hour then called back and they were closed.  Got charged and no food was delivered.

name: Shayna Fennoff
text:
the place was absolutely disgusting and when i went to the "manager on duty" they basically said too bad. TERRIBLE customer service.
don't bother going there.

name: Andrew Staddon
text: Online orders are never ready when I pick up food here...even though the online order system says it should be ready.  We're talking 10+ minutes waiting each time even though it's "ready"
